reviews.review_text: Mix Is ROUGH the first two songs Gets better after that. Great versions of It Must Have Been the Roses and The Race Is On (1st electric since 10/19/74) which seem to have new life following the acoustic shows. On The Road Again (1st electric since 12/1/66) is not so tight but the Jack-A-Roe makes up for it. First Satisfaction too! Well played for the time.
